If you don't already have one, get a wideband air fuel meter and read the
following:

http://www.thesamba.com/vw/forum/viewtopic.php?t=293837&postdays=0&postorder=
asc&start=0

I realise that it is mostly about carbs, but John Connolly's insights on A/F
ratios are essential reading for tuning carbs or FI.
